{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01VYMPdAHh6CsrZrSq6u43qq","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I see two issues:\n\n1. **`isLast` is not available** - In Qute, within a `{#for}` loop, you use `hasNext` and `count` instead of `isLast`. The syntax is `{#if !hasNext}` instead of `{#if !isLast}`.\n2. **404 for `/owners/find`** etc - The OwnerResource has `@Path(\"/owners\")`, but the `WelcomeResource` has `@Path(\"/\")` which might conflict. Also, the `findOwners` template might not be found.\n\nLet me also check what's wrong with the 404:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2157,"cache_read_input_tokens":144050,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":2157,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":266},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86a09403-f8e6-4dd1-bd75-9998012ce328","uuid":"ecebfff1-f46f-48ba-917b-17dd47369124"}
