{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01K1cWXSsiUgSLpxiCjwWDLK","type":"tool_result","content":"  % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  Current\n                                 Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  Speed\n\r  0     0    0     0    0     0      0      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:--     0*   Trying ::1:33570...\n* Connected to localhost (::1) port 33570 (#0)\n> GET /owners/1 HTTP/1.1\r\n> Host: localhost:33570\r\n> User-Agent: curl/7.76.1\r\n> Accept: */*\r\n> \r\n* Mark bundle as not supporting multiuse\n< HTTP/1.1 404 Not Found\r\n< content-type: text/html; charset=utf-8\r\n< content-length: 53\r\n< \r\n{ [53 bytes data]\n\r100    53  100    53    0     0  10600      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:-- 10600\n* Connection #0 to host localhost left intact\n<html><body><h1>Resource not found</h1></body></html>","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86a09403-f8e6-4dd1-bd75-9998012ce328","uuid":"24470424-454d-4967-bc41-0f7806289473"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01N4dfkx9kfhvpokrmZMtV59","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The 404 is strange. This means the JAX-RS framework is not finding a matching resource. Looking at this more carefully, the issue is likely a conflict between `WelcomeResource` at `@Path(\"/\")` and `VetResource` at `@Path(\"/\")`. Both have `@Path(\"/\")` as their class-level path. In JAX-RS Reactive (RESTEasy Reactive), there may be issues when multiple resource classes share the same root path.\n\nBut the `OwnerResource` at `@Path(\"/owners\")` should not conflict. Let me check if the class is actually being registered. The problem might be that the class doesn't have `@ApplicationScoped` or isn't being picked up as a CDI bean for injection:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":975,"cache_read_input_tokens":147590,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":975,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":312},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86a09403-f8e6-4dd1-bd75-9998012ce328","uuid":"55d709db-b8d7-44d8-b1fb-80052eb3490a"}
