{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01KyoEjMfpBZAcSrawiN6rr8","type":"tool_result","content":"    25→\n    26→\n    27→def test_owners_list():\n    28→    \"\"\"Test listing all owners.\"\"\"\n    29→    r = requests.get(f\"{BASE_URL}/owners?lastName=\", timeout=10)\n    30→    assert r.status_code == 200, f\"Owners list returned {r.status_code}\"\n    31→    assert \"Franklin\" in r.text or \"George\" in r.text, \"Owners list missing expected data\"\n    32→    print(\"PASS: Owners list loads successfully with data\")\n    33→\n    34→\n    35→def test_owner_details():\n    36→    \"\"\"Test viewing a specific owner.\"\"\"\n    37→    r = requests.get(f\"{BASE_URL}/owners/1\", timeout=10)\n    38→    assert r.status_code == 200, f\"Owner details returned {r.status_code}\"\n    39→    assert \"George\" in r.text or \"Franklin\" in r.text, \"Owner details missing expected data\"\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86a09403-f8e6-4dd1-bd75-9998012ce328","uuid":"aed48ff5-5883-4093-b379-930c1a52a350"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01JoHTGQDNvbpwkaiGrPzYR1","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `test_owners_list` expects \"Franklin\" or \"George\" to be on the first page. The first owner is George Franklin (ID=1). With an empty lastName search, 10 owners should match. 5 per page. Let me check what our repository returns:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":473,"cache_read_input_tokens":63927,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":473,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":188},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86a09403-f8e6-4dd1-bd75-9998012ce328","uuid":"194187a6-e4ac-41d6-902a-df9e10672307"}
