{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_012SVAV5fccN35xZ7uFHHkQn","type":"tool_result","content":"src/main/resources/templates/createOrUpdatePetForm.html:3:  <h2>{#if isNew}New Pet{#else}Pet{/if}</h2>\nsrc/main/resources/templates/createOrUpdatePetForm.html:5:  <form action=\"{#if isNew}/owners/{owner.id}/pets/new{#else}/owners/{owner.id}/pets/{pet.id}/edit{/if}\" method=\"post\" class=\"form-horizontal\">\nsrc/main/resources/templates/createOrUpdatePetForm.html:30:        <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">{#if isNew}Add Pet{#else}Update Pet{/if}</button>\nsrc/main/resources/templates/createOrUpdateOwnerForm.html:3:  <h2>{#if isNew}New Owner{#else}Owner{/if}</h2>\nsrc/main/resources/templates/createOrUpdateOwnerForm.html:4:  <form action=\"{#if isNew}/owners/new{#else}/owners/{owner.id}/edit{/if}\" method=\"post\" class=\"form-horizontal\">\nsrc/main/resources/templates/createOrUpdateOwnerForm.html:40:        <button class=\"btn btn-primary\" type=\"submit\">{#if isNew}Add Owner{#else}Update Owner{/if}</button>"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86a09403-f8e6-4dd1-bd75-9998012ce328","uuid":"9cd77ca1-5533-407a-a721-85b482e0e8aa"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01YAaci9958TNdVZ3jsND8ik","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The `isNew` key is always provided by all the resource methods that use those templates (I verified in OwnerResource earlier), so those should be fine. Let me also check the `owner.lastName` reference in the findOwners template - when we create `new Owner()`, the lastName field might be null which could cause a Qute error:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":827,"cache_read_input_tokens":74111,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":827,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":199},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86a09403-f8e6-4dd1-bd75-9998012ce328","uuid":"39cc9d03-f372-4871-9dd2-02aa8cd3fd4e"}
