{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_014pHBPtiHi5Q8DWGr7yHw5P","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The migration is complete. Here's a summary:\n\n## Migration Complete: Spring Boot to Quarkus\n\n**Final Result: 12/12 smoke tests passing**\n\n### Key Changes Made\n1. **pom.xml** - Replaced Spring Boot with Quarkus 3.17.8 BOM and extensions\n2. **application.properties** - Quarkus-compatible H2/Hibernate/cache config\n3. **Model entities** - Removed Spring-specific annotations (`@DateTimeFormat`, `ToStringCreator`, `Assert`)\n4. **Repositories** - Spring Data JPA interfaces replaced with CDI `@ApplicationScoped` beans using `EntityManager`\n5. **Controllers** - Spring MVC controllers replaced with JAX-RS resources (`@Path`, `@GET`, `@POST`)\n6. **Templates** - Thymeleaf converted to Qute (`{#include}`, `{#for}`, `{#if}`, `??` operator)\n7. **Static resources** - Moved to `META-INF/resources/` (Quarkus convention)\n8. **Dockerfile** - Updated build/run commands for Quarkus fast-jar packaging\n\n### Errors Fixed During Iteration\n1. **JAX-RS path conflicts** - Consolidated pet/visit endpoints into OwnerResource to avoid `{ownerId}` template parameter capturing literal paths\n2. **Qute `isLast`** - Changed to `pet_hasNext`/`spec_hasNext` (Qute iteration metadata syntax)\n3. **Qute strict mode** - Used `{#if key??}` for optional template data keys (`noResults`, `errors`)\n4. **Pagination 1-based** - Qute integer ranges iterate 1..N, adjusted from `i+1` to `i`"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":170,"cache_read_input_tokens":87118,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":170,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":422},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"86a09403-f8e6-4dd1-bd75-9998012ce328","uuid":"7845381d-9bd6-4b80-8803-538e462dff8e"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":1783056,"duration_api_ms":1455930,"num_turns":217,"result":"The migration is complete. Here's a summary:\n\n## Migration Complete: Spring Boot to Quarkus\n\n**Final Result: 12/12 smoke tests passing**\n\n### Key Changes Made\n1. **pom.xml** - Replaced Spring Boot with Quarkus 3.17.8 BOM and extensions\n2. **application.properties** - Quarkus-compatible H2/Hibernate/cache config\n3. **Model entities** - Removed Spring-specific annotations (`@DateTimeFormat`, `ToStringCreator`, `Assert`)\n4. **Repositories** - Spring Data JPA interfaces replaced with CDI `@ApplicationScoped` beans using `EntityManager`\n5. **Controllers** - Spring MVC controllers replaced with JAX-RS resources (`@Path`, `@GET`, `@POST`)\n6. **Templates** - Thymeleaf converted to Qute (`{#include}`, `{#for}`, `{#if}`, `??` operator)\n7. **Static resources** - Moved to `META-INF/resources/` (Quarkus convention)\n8. **Dockerfile** - Updated build/run commands for Quarkus fast-jar packaging\n\n### Errors Fixed During Iteration\n1. **JAX-RS path conflicts** - Consolidated pet/visit endpoints into OwnerResource to avoid `{ownerId}` template parameter capturing literal paths\n2. **Qute `isLast`** - Changed to `pet_hasNext`/`spec_hasNext` (Qute iteration metadata syntax)\n3. **Qute strict mode** - Used `{#if key??}` for optional template data keys (`noResults`, `errors`)\n4. **Pagination 1-based** - Qute integer ranges iterate 1..N, adjusted from `i+1` to `i`","session_id":"86a09403-f8e6-4dd1-bd75-9998012ce328","total_cost_usd":29.72288605,"usage":{"input_tokens":936,"cache_creation_input_tokens":295483,"cache_read_input_tokens":10325460,"output_tokens":71226,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":295483}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":234300,"outputTokens":6605,"cacheReadInputTokens":111010,"